name: London Rock and Roll Stage Show Wembley 1991 DVD
description: This is the DVD of the 1991 Wembley Rock'n'Roll Stage show. It featured rockabilly legend Ronnie Dawson, Doo Wop Legends The Cleftones, The Flamingos and The Jive Five plus Rock'n'Roll great Jimmy Jones. Not forgetting young acts Sonny West and Tiger Lily. The MD is Randall Lee Rose of Londons Capital Gold.
